<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="12Dec1917"><font color="red">12 December 1917</font>, <cite>Letters II</cite> (JJ to Claud Sykes): Many thanks for your kind words about my book. You will receive the second episode on the 20th. Can you arrange with Mr Goldschmidt for a few afternoons as his machine is better. The episode is only half as long as the other. Better arrange in advance &hellip; PS needless to add I rec&apos;d safely the typescript: thanks.</div>
